title: mv多世界问题
txt_content:
在1.12.2的版本中输入/mv import pm normal打算导入存档，但是插件提示我

an internal error occurred when attempting to perform this commad.
Details were printed to the sever console and logs,please add that to your bug report.

说是后台和日志给我生成错误报告，但是就是没有生成出来，请问这该怎么解决？
